name: Valvoline Oil Can Fine Art Silk Screen Print
description:
Warhol had soup cans, we have oil cans. A playful, tongue-in-cheek take-off on one of pop art's most famous canned products. This three color silk screen fine art print is handed printed by artist Jonathon Kimbrell, measuring 16" x 20 1/4" on acid free Accent opaque white 100# cover stock. Print comes signed and numbered in a strict edition of of only 20 prints, and comes stamped on the back.

Print will ship within five (5) business day after purchase, well-protected inside of a sturdy cardboard tube.

Once this print sells out, no other editions will be offered.

name: Kennedy '64 Silk Screen Print
description:

Three color hand silk screened print on 12" x 18" French Madero Beach Speckletone 100lb cover stock.

S/N edition of only 25 with certificate of authenticity (COA).

Print will ship well-protected in sturdy cardboard tube with 3-5 business days after purchase. International purchasers are responsible for any and all additional import taxes/duties/tariffs/fees that may incur.

Please feel free to ask any questions prior to purchase.

name: "We Are Modern" Silk Screen Print (Test Pressing Edition)
description:
"We Are Modern," hand-printed three color silk screen on 100lb acid free cover stock. Print measure 12 x 18 inches, and comes stamped, signed with certificate of authenticity (COA).

*Prior to full print run, the artist will often produce a few artist proof or test pressing editions of the design, to ensure the print meets quality standards. These artist proof/test pressing editions are often more valuable and sought after than the numbered editions in the print series. What also makes these editions collectible is they often have slight variances or imperfections within the print, making each print unique. 

Print will ship in sturdy mailer tube, well protected, within 3-5 business days of purchase date.

Please feel free to ask any questions prior to purchase.

*PLEASE NOTE: International purchasers are responsible for any and all additional import taxes/duties/tariffs/fees that may incur.
